data.description: 2.875% Interest rate ASSUMABLE LOAN for the qualified BUYER!!    Welcome to a top-floor live/work loft exuding exceptional style. The layout seamlessly integrates the kitchen, living, office, and bedroom spaces, maintaining an airy ambiance. Abundant natural light streams through expansive industrial windows. A wood-burning fireplace adds coziness, while the gourmet kitchen boasts granite counters, maple cabinets, and premium stainless steel appliances. Contemporary design is evident in the smartly crafted walls, shelves, and blackout shades.....The bedroom encompasses a spacious walk-in closet, while the bathroom showcases upscale European Duravit fixtures. Convenience is optimized with concealed stacked Miele washer and dryer. Surrounding the loft, custom built-in storage includes an 8-foot-tall entry cabinet, wooden counters, shelves, drawers, and even a designated wine cellar spot. This home comes with an assigned parking space that has an Electric Vehicle Charging Station.....The building offers a rich lifestyle with amenities such as an open-air lounge patio, garden pool, and relaxing spa. Residents enjoy access to a gym, ample covered guest parking, a dog run, and 24-hour gated security. More than a mere loft, this is an innovative, modern, luxury home within an established, vibrant community complex.
